ygData.messageBody:
If your on a new server then do aviaks... Fastest way i know is in lake rathe
the two aviak spawn right by arena.... I never died there and I was the
second level 50 necro and the first one was my hunting partner and we hunted
all the same shit...Aviaks are only really good fro necros if you got the
spawn alone though.  SO it works good on a new server.

Xurtin Shadowreaver
Retired 50necromancer
